### ðŸ” Sliding Window Template (Substring Problems)

```python
def sliding_window(s):
    left = 0
    window = {}
    for right in range(len(s)):
        char = s[right]
        # update window
        while invalid(window):  # condition to shrink window
            window[s[left]] -= 1
            left += 1
    return result
```

